\[%mdk-data-line={105}

\[%mdk-data-line={108}
\ln \left( x-\sqrt(x^2 - 1) * \frac{x+\sqrt(x^2 - 1)}{x+\sqrt(x^2 - 1)}\right) = \ln \left(\frac{1}{x+\sqrt(x^2 - 1)}\right) = \ln(x + \sqrt(x^2 - 1))
\]%mdk
